# Third-party notices

This file records external material that AIRAS adapts or redistributes,
beyond normal package dependencies (which carry their own licenses).

Entries are required whenever content is adapted from externally licensed
material — including the curated engineering notes under
`backend/src/airas/resources/knowledge/` (see that directory's README for
the authoring rules). Notes written originally and merely informed by
public documentation list their references in their own `sources:`
frontmatter and need no entry here.

Format per entry:

- <path in this repository>
  Origin: <project name, URL, version/commit if applicable>
  License: <license of the original>
  Changes: <summary of how the material was adapted>

